cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.HC 

This paper deals with image quality and its impact on peer-to-peer marketplaces. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves user-generated content and trust, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the design of marketplaces, which could be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
